**File:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/lol/src/components/action_panel/actions_dropdown.tsx`, lines 172-178 and 185-188

When `openSubmenu` fires, it sets `submenuDirection` to `'enter'` and simultaneously sets `submenu` state. React batches these, so the next render shows the **new submenu content** with the `slide-left` animation. This means you see the **new content** sliding in from the right -- which is correct.

