**File:** `/Users/anotonio.silva/antonio/lol/src/components/action_panel/actions_dropdown.tsx`

The back button is rendered outside the `renderSections` loop and has no `data-dropdown-index` attribute. ArrowUp/ArrowDown navigation only cycles through items with indices 0..N-1. The back button is completely unreachable via keyboard arrows -- it can only be clicked with a mouse.

